The '''Baronis''' were a family that lived on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Peekoine]]. The group consisted of the main family, as well as [[Madame Baronis]] and an especially paranoid old man. The main family was vacationing when a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] were visiting [[Peekoine]] searching for two [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]].

